      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, drivable vehicle that gets the job done? This car could be just what you need! It's in fair condition \u2014 fully functional and road-ready, though it does show noticeable signs of wear both inside and out. The exterior has some cosmetic blemishes and the interior reflects its years of use, but there's solid value here for a budget-conscious buyer who doesn't mind a little character. A great opportunity to get behind the wheel without a hefty price tag!",
