    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition at a honest, competitive price. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 you'll find only minor surface scratches and perhaps a small scuff or two consistent with normal everyday use, but no significant dents, rust, or paint damage. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with no major tears, stains, or broken components; everything functions as expected. Mechanically, the car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, transmission shifts properly, and all major systems including brakes, steering, and suspension are in solid working order. This is a dependable vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner without requiring immediate repairs.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition, and it genuinely earns that designation. The exterior is immaculate \u2014 the paint retains its original deep gloss with absolutely no fading, chips, or scratches visible from any angle. The interior is equally impressive, with all surfaces, upholstery, and trim pieces looking as though they just left the showroom floor. Mechanically, the car is in excellent shape: the engine runs smoothly and quietly, all systems function exactly as intended, and there are no warning lights or known issues of any kind. The tires have substantial tread remaining, the brakes are responsive and solid, and every electronic feature works flawlessly. Service records are up to date, and the vehicle has been meticulously maintained throughout its life. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been treated with exceptional care \u2014 a buyer can expect to drive away with complete confidence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable vehicle with plenty of potential? This car is honestly showing its age and wear \u2014 it has some mechanical issues and cosmetic imperfections that need attention, so it's best suited for a handy buyer, a project enthusiast, or someone who needs basic transportation on a tight budget. What it lacks in polish, it makes up for in affordability! Priced to reflect its current condition, this is a great opportunity for the right buyer who knows what they're getting into and wants a deal.",
      "price": 6500.0,
