    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\u2728 Showroom-Quality Mint Condition \u2014 Truly Turn Heads Everywhere You Go! \u2728 This vehicle is the real deal \u2014 a genuine mint-condition find that lives up to every bit of the hype! The exterior is absolutely flawless, sporting a gleaming, scratch-free finish that looks like it just rolled off the lot. Inside, the cabin is immaculate \u2014 clean, fresh, and beautifully maintained with no wear, stains, or odors to speak of. Under the hood, everything is in top-notch working order, running smoothly and confidently. If you've been searching for a vehicle you can be truly proud of, this is it. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations! \ud83c\udf1f",
