      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a fair-condition car. Buyers should expect a vehicle that is functional and drivable but shows clear signs of age and use throughout. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, small dents, and some paint fading that are consistent with years of regular use \u2014 this is not a cosmetically pristine vehicle. The interior shows moderate wear including some fading on the seats, minor scuffs on the dashboard, and general signs of daily use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though buyers should anticipate that some components may be approaching the end of their service life and budget accordingly for potential near-term maintenance. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection so buyers have a full picture of what they're getting. This is an honest listing for a car priced to reflect its actual condition \u2014 a practical, usable vehicle for someone who values function over appearance.",
